struct vsip::impl::Rt_block_copy_from_ptr_impl<Dim,Block,true,false>
File: ../../../vsip/core/block_copy.hpp

Specialization for const blocks (with complex value type).

Non-modifiable blocks cannot be written to. However, Ext_data and Rt_ext_data use a run-time value (sync) to determine if a block will be written.
